00:53:17.349 --> 00:53:18.880
Well, what happens if you want
to move?

00:53:18.880 --> 00:53:22.090
If you want to move you're
going to sell the house.

00:53:22.090 --> 00:53:24.918
The house is no longer
collateral, so if you want to

00:53:24.918 --> 00:53:27.579
move you have to undo the
promise to the bank.

00:53:27.579 --> 00:53:30.947
So if in year 5 just after
you're making your payment of 8

00:53:30.947 --> 00:53:34.018
dollars and 5 cents in year 5
