00:53:42.159 --> 00:53:47.173
So that's why this remaining
balance is such an important

00:53:47.173 --> 00:53:47.980
number.
 

00:53:47.980 --> 00:53:51.597
So it allows people to leave
their house and pay off their

00:53:51.597 --> 00:53:54.579
mortgage by paying off the
remaining balance.

00:53:54.579 --> 00:53:57.186
You wouldn't want them to pay
100 if they left because they've

00:53:57.186 --> 00:53:57.869
made payments.
 

00:53:57.869 --> 00:54:00.940
You notice that the payment
