That would have a present value
of 100.

00:54:09.539 --> 00:54:11.320
If you're not paying the 100 at
the end,

00:54:11.320 --> 00:54:13.000
but just making a level payment
all the way through,

00:54:13.000 --> 00:54:15.384
the payment you have to make
every year better be more than

00:54:15.384 --> 00:54:16.760
7,
so it's 8.

00:54:16.760 --> 00:54:21.016
So this 8 - 7 is sort of what
you're paying down of your

00:54:21.016 --> 00:54:22.409
mortgage, right?
 

